arts.ttl: Liechtenstein vs Belgium – Match preview and team news
arts.sum: Liechtenstein and Belgium meet for the first time in an anticipated World Cup qualifier at Rheinpark Stadion on Thursday. The hosts will search for a maiden point in Group J, while the visitors aim to extend their resurgence under new coach Rudi Garcia.
